                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "Before Swift-DocC 6.0, article-only documentation catalogs require one of the articles to be marked as a ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "code" : "TechnologyRoot",
                  "type" : "codeVoice"
                },
                {
